{
  "stem": "2966.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't get any food from them, even less than from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, there was a lot of Poles and Russians in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were in pretty good shape, physically.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They went through the villages, and they used to rob the Germans of food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- being very hungry, I went to the village too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I thought, I'll get some food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But, being a schlimazel, me and about 30 other guys like me were caught again by the Germans that must have come back to a to the village to sort through the town.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were caught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was not SS anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was just a soldiers, the Whermacht, the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the civilian population was complaining that we are robbing them, so they took us back into prison or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They didn't know what to do with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had no place for us, so they turned us over to the civilian authorities.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Civilian authorities didn't know what to do with us, so they were taking us from village to village, from town to town, and that's how I worked.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "From May 1 to May 6, I was walking, and walking, and walking, and all 30 guys of us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, the night of May 6, I decided with another fellow, with another Polack, to run away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we weren't really watched anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we ran away, and we were going towards the front.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The front we knew was very close because you could hear the shooting and the guns very clearly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we were passing by-- must have been headquarters of German Army yet-- the guy on the guards, the guard soldier stopped us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where you going?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he put us back in, took us back into prison.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
